data.description: Nestled on a generous 2-acre lot, this property provides the tranquility of rural living without the restrictions of an HOA. The well-designed floor plan features 3 bed/2 bath, each offering ample space and natural light. The master bedroom comes complete with walk-in closet and its own ensuite bathroom and soaking tub. The living area is perfect for both relaxation and entertaining guests. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, making meal preparation a breeze. With 2-Acres the possibilities are endless. Create your dream garden or outdoor recreational space or simply enjoy the beauty of nature, this property offers it.
